{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":765,"text":"Well, you know, sometimes"},{"time":2276,"text":"the most important things come\nin the smallest packages."},{"time":5258,"text":"I am going to try to convince you,\nin the 15 minutes I have,"},{"time":8847,"text":"that microbes have a lot to say\nabout questions such as,"},{"time":13100,"text":"\"Are we alone?\""},{"time":14998,"text":"and they can tell us more about\nnot only life in our solar system"},{"time":20223,"text":"but also maybe beyond,"},{"time":22100,"text":"and this is why I am tracking them down\nin the most impossible places on Earth,"},{"time":27397,"text":"in extreme environments where conditions"},{"time":29766,"text":"are really pushing them\nto the brink of survival."},{"time":32450,"text":"Actually, sometimes me too,\nwhen I'm trying to follow them too close."},{"time":35704,"text":"But here's the thing:"},{"time":37521,"text":"We are the only advanced civilization\nin the solar system,"},{"time":43134,"text":"but that doesn't mean that there is\nno microbial life nearby."},{"time":46878,"text":"In fact, the planets\nand moons you see here"},{"time":50663,"text":"could host life -- all of them --\nand we know that,"},{"time":54633,"text":"and it's a strong possibility."},{"time":57482,"text":"And if we were going to find life\non those moons and planets,"},{"time":62135,"text":"then we would answer questions such as,"},{"time":65151,"text":"are we alone in the solar system?"},{"time":67287,"text":"Where are we coming from?"},{"time":69256,"text":"Do we have family in the neighborhood?"},{"time":72233,"text":"Is there life beyond our solar system?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76157,"text":"And we can ask all those questions\nbecause there has been a revolution"},{"time":80244,"text":"in our understanding\nof what a habitable planet is,"},{"time":84520,"text":"and today, a habitable planet is a planet"},{"time":87860,"text":"that has a zone where\nwater can stay stable,"},{"time":92193,"text":"but to me this is a horizontal\ndefinition of habitability,"},{"time":95922,"text":"because it involves a distance to a star,"},{"time":98197,"text":"but there is another\ndimension to habitability,"},{"time":101169,"text":"and this is a vertical dimension."},{"time":103840,"text":"Think of it as"},{"time":107527,"text":"conditions in the subsurface of a planet\nwhere you are very far away from a sun,"},{"time":114210,"text":"but you still have water,\nenergy, nutrients,"},{"time":117353,"text":"which for some of them means food,"},{"time":119304,"text":"and a protection."},{"time":121207,"text":"And when you look at the Earth,"},{"time":123251,"text":"very far away from any sunlight,\ndeep in the ocean,"},{"time":127796,"text":"you have life thriving"},{"time":129665,"text":"and it uses only chemistry\nfor life processes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133676,"text":"So when you think of it \nat that point, all walls collapse."},{"time":139326,"text":"You have no limitations, basically."},{"time":141600,"text":"And if you have been looking\nat the headlines lately,"},{"time":144160,"text":"then you will see that we have\ndiscovered a subsurface ocean"},{"time":147120,"text":"on Europa, on Ganymede,\non Enceladus, on Titan,"},{"time":150989,"text":"and now we are finding a geyser\nand hot springs on Enceladus,"},{"time":153923,"text":"Our solar system is turning\ninto a giant spa."},{"time":157978,"text":"For anybody who has gone to a spa\nknows how much microbes like that, right?"},{"time":161864,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":163582,"text":"So at that point, think also about Mars."},{"time":167111,"text":"There is no life possible\nat the surface of Mars today,"},{"time":170478,"text":"but it might still be hiding underground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173729,"text":"So, we have been making progress\nin our understanding of habitability,"},{"time":179339,"text":"but we also have been making progress\nin our understanding"},{"time":182111,"text":"of what the signatures\nof life are on Earth."},{"time":185687,"text":"And you can have what we call\norganic molecules,"},{"time":188543,"text":"and these are the bricks of life,"},{"time":190470,"text":"and you can have fossils,"},{"time":192350,"text":"and you can minerals, biominerals,"},{"time":195253,"text":"which is due to the reaction\nbetween bacteria and rocks,"},{"time":198643,"text":"and of course you can have\ngases in the atmosphere."},{"time":201777,"text":"And when you look at those\ntiny green algae"},{"time":203983,"text":"on the right of the slide here,"},{"time":205934,"text":"they are the direct descendants\nof those who have been pumping oxygen"},{"time":209450,"text":"a billion years ago\nin the atmosphere of the Earth."},{"time":211843,"text":"When they did that, they poisoned\n90 percent of the life"},{"time":214465,"text":"at the surface of the Earth,"},{"time":215987,"text":"but they are the reason why\nyou are breathing this air today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220740,"text":"But as much as our understanding grows\nof all of these things,"},{"time":225925,"text":"there is one question\nwe still cannot answer,"},{"time":228851,"text":"and this is, where are we coming from?"},{"time":231126,"text":"And you know, it's getting worse,"},{"time":232844,"text":"because we won't be able\nto find the physical evidence"},{"time":235886,"text":"of where we are coming from\non this planet,"},{"time":238440,"text":"and the reason being is that anything that\nis older than four billion years is gone."},{"time":244130,"text":"All record is gone,"},{"time":245754,"text":"erased by plate tectonics and erosion."},{"time":249632,"text":"This is what I call the Earth's\nbiological horizon."},{"time":253184,"text":"Beyond this horizon we don't know\nwhere we are coming from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256667,"text":"So is everything lost? Well, maybe not."},{"time":259593,"text":"And we might be able to find\nevidence of our own origin"},{"time":263308,"text":"in the most unlikely place,\nand this place in Mars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267929,"text":"How is this possible?"},{"time":269420,"text":"Well clearly at the beginning\nof the solar system,"},{"time":272201,"text":"Mars and the Earth were bombarded\nby giant asteroids and comets,"},{"time":277169,"text":"and there were ejecta\nfrom these impacts all over the place."},{"time":280327,"text":"Earth and Mars kept throwing rocks\nat each other for a very long time."},{"time":284187,"text":"Pieces of rocks landed on the Earth."},{"time":286230,"text":"Pieces of the Earth landed on Mars."},{"time":288181,"text":"So clearly, those two planets may have\nbeen seeded by the same material."},{"time":293359,"text":"So yeah, maybe Granddady is sitting\nthere on the surface and waiting for us."},{"time":298659,"text":"But that also means that we can go to Mars\nand try to find traces of our own origin."},{"time":306190,"text":"Mars may hold that secret for us."},{"time":308442,"text":"This is why Mars is so special to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311150,"text":"But for that to happen,"},{"time":313160,"text":"Mars needed to be habitable\nat the time when conditions were right."},{"time":318544,"text":"So was Mars habitable?"},{"time":320400,"text":"We have a number of missions\ntelling us exactly the same thing today."},{"time":324254,"text":"At the time when life\nappeared on the Earth,"},{"time":327992,"text":"Mars did have an ocean,\nit had volcanoes, it had lakes,"},{"time":332830,"text":"and it had deltas like the beautiful\npicture you see here."},{"time":335673,"text":"This picture was sent by the Curiosity \nrover only a few weeks ago."},{"time":339460,"text":"It shows the remnants of a delta,\nand this picture tells us something:"},{"time":343142,"text":"water was abundant"},{"time":345096,"text":"and stayed founting at the surface\nfor a very long time."},{"time":347757,"text":"This is good news for life."},{"time":349568,"text":"Life chemistry takes a long time\nto actually happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352990,"text":"So this is extremely good news,"},{"time":354507,"text":"but does that mean that if we go there,\nlife will be easy to find on Mars?"},{"time":358127,"text":"Not necessarily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360010,"text":"Here's what happened:"},{"time":361861,"text":"At the time when life exploded\nat the surface of the Earth,"},{"time":365230,"text":"then everything went south for Mars,"},{"time":367369,"text":"literally."},{"time":368901,"text":"The atmosphere was\nstripped away by solar winds,"},{"time":372472,"text":"Mars lost its magnetosphere,"},{"time":374775,"text":"and then cosmic rays and U.V.\nbombarded the surface"},{"time":379187,"text":"and water escaped to space\nand went underground."},{"time":383410,"text":"So if we want to be able to understand,"},{"time":386501,"text":"if we want to be able to find those traces\nof the signatures of life"},{"time":391430,"text":"at the surface of Mars, if they are there,"},{"time":393644,"text":"we need to understand what was\nthe impact of each of these events"},{"time":396831,"text":"on the preservation of its record."},{"time":400484,"text":"Only then will we be able\nto know where those signatures are hiding,"},{"time":405314,"text":"and only then will we be able\nto send our rover to the right places"},{"time":408997,"text":"where we can sample those rocks\nthat may be telling us something"},{"time":412146,"text":"really important about who we are,"},{"time":414862,"text":"or, if not, maybe telling us\nthat somewhere, independently,"},{"time":418972,"text":"life has appeared on another planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421828,"text":"So to do that, it's easy."},{"time":424336,"text":"You only need to go back\n3.5 billion years ago"},{"time":427894,"text":"in the past of a planet."},{"time":430285,"text":"We just need a time machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432909,"text":"Easy, right?"},{"time":435103,"text":"Well, actually, it is."},{"time":436673,"text":"Look around you -- that's planet Earth."},{"time":438574,"text":"This is our time machine."},{"time":440618,"text":"Geologists are using it\nto go back in the past of our own planet."},{"time":444788,"text":"I am using it a little bit differently."},{"time":446971,"text":"I use planet Earth to go\nin very extreme environments"},{"time":449966,"text":"where conditions were similar\nto those of Mars"},{"time":452868,"text":"at the time when the climate changed,"},{"time":454865,"text":"and there I'm trying \nto understand what happened."},{"time":457745,"text":"What are the signatures of life?"},{"time":459439,"text":"What is left? How are we going to find it?"},{"time":462272,"text":"So for one moment now\nI'm going to take you with me"},{"time":465276,"text":"on a trip into that time machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468130,"text":"And now, what you see here,\nwe are at 4,500 meters in the Andes,"},{"time":472865,"text":"but in fact we are less than a billion\nyears after the Earth and Mars formed."},{"time":479594,"text":"The Earth and Mars will have looked\npretty much exactly like that --"},{"time":483285,"text":"volcanoes everywhere,\nevaporating lakes everywhere,"},{"time":486796,"text":"minerals, hot springs,"},{"time":490103,"text":"and then you see those mounds\non the shore of those lakes?"},{"time":493934,"text":"Those are built by the descendants\nof the first organisms"},{"time":497394,"text":"that gave us the first fossil on Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500496,"text":"But if we want to understand what's \ngoing on, we need to go a little further."},{"time":504555,"text":"And the other thing about those sites"},{"time":506470,"text":"is that exactly like on Mars\nthree and a half billion years ago,"},{"time":509946,"text":"the climate is changing very fast,\nand water and ice are disappearing."},{"time":514463,"text":"But we need to go back to that time\nwhen everything changed on Mars,"},{"time":517678,"text":"and to do that, we need to go higher."},{"time":520441,"text":"Why is that?"},{"time":521858,"text":"Because when you go higher,"},{"time":523215,"text":"the atmosphere is getting thinner,\nit's getting more unstable,"},{"time":526337,"text":"the temperature is getting cooler,\nand you have a lot more U.V. radiation."},{"time":531648,"text":"Basically,"},{"time":532457,"text":"you are getting to those conditions\non Mars when everything changed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538340,"text":"So I was not promising anything about\na leisurely trip on the time machine."},{"time":544837,"text":"You are not going to be sitting\nin that time machine."},{"time":547371,"text":"You have to haul 1,000 pounds\nof equipment to the summit"},{"time":550399,"text":"of this 20,000-foot volcano\nin the Andes here."},{"time":554184,"text":"That's about 6,000 meters."},{"time":556784,"text":"And you also have to sleep\non 42-degree slopes"},{"time":560407,"text":"and really hope that there won't\nbe any earthquake that night."},{"time":563518,"text":"But when we get to the summit,\nwe actually find the lake we came for."},{"time":568464,"text":"At this altitude, this lake is\nexperiencing exactly the same conditions"},{"time":573126,"text":"as those on Mars\nthree and a half billion years ago."},{"time":576245,"text":"And now we have to change our voyage"},{"time":579170,"text":"into an inner voyage inside that lake,"},{"time":581890,"text":"and to do that, we have to remove\nour mountain gear"},{"time":585541,"text":"and actually don suits and go for it."},{"time":590277,"text":"But at the time we enter that lake,\nat the very moment we enter that lake,"},{"time":594452,"text":"we are stepping back"},{"time":596380,"text":"three and a half billion years\nin the past of another planet,"},{"time":599561,"text":"and then we are going to get\nthe answer came for."},{"time":604511,"text":"Life is everywhere, absolutely everywhere."},{"time":607633,"text":"Everything you see in this picture\nis a living organism."},{"time":610953,"text":"Maybe not so the diver,\nbut everything else."},{"time":615626,"text":"But this picture is very deceiving."},{"time":618853,"text":"Life is abundant in those lakes,"},{"time":621523,"text":"but like in many places on Earth \nright now and due to climate change,"},{"time":625630,"text":"there is a huge loss in biodiversity."},{"time":628744,"text":"In the samples that we took back home,"},{"time":631740,"text":"36 percent of the bacteria in those lakes\nwere composed of three species,"},{"time":637556,"text":"and those three species are the ones\nthat have survived so far."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641375,"text":"Here's another lake,\nright next to the first one."},{"time":644162,"text":"The red color you see here\nis not due to minerals."},{"time":647830,"text":"It's actually due to the presence\nof a tiny algae."},{"time":651151,"text":"In this region, the U.V. radiation\nis really nasty."},{"time":655660,"text":"Anywhere on Earth, 11\nis considered to be extreme."},{"time":659129,"text":"During U.V. storms there,\nthe U.V. Index reaches 43."},{"time":663730,"text":"SPF 30 is not going to do anything \nto you over there,"},{"time":667976,"text":"and the water is so\ntransparent in those lakes"},{"time":671342,"text":"that the algae has\nnowhere to hide, really,"},{"time":674675,"text":"and so they are developing\ntheir own sunscreen,"},{"time":676965,"text":"and this is the red color you see."},{"time":678749,"text":"But they can adapt only so far,"},{"time":681310,"text":"and then when all the water\nis gone from the surface,"},{"time":683788,"text":"microbes have only one solution left:"},{"time":686388,"text":"They go underground."},{"time":688246,"text":"And those microbes, the rocks\nyou see in that slide here,"},{"time":691171,"text":"well, they are actually\nliving inside rocks"},{"time":694391,"text":"and they are using the protection\nof the translucence of the rocks"},{"time":697585,"text":"to get the good part of the U.V."},{"time":699382,"text":"and discard the part that could\nactually damage their DNA."},{"time":703126,"text":"And this is why we are taking our rover"},{"time":705401,"text":"to train them to search \nfor life on Mars in these areas,"},{"time":708977,"text":"because if there was life on Mars\nthree and a half billion years ago,"},{"time":712714,"text":"it had to use the same strategy\nto actually protect itself."},{"time":717864,"text":"Now, it is pretty obvious"},{"time":720242,"text":"that going to extreme environments\nis helping us very much"},{"time":723770,"text":"for the exploration of Mars \nand to prepare missions."},{"time":727761,"text":"So far, it has helped us to understand\nthe geology of Mars."},{"time":732100,"text":"It has helped to understand the past\nclimate of Mars and its evolution,"},{"time":736221,"text":"but also its habitability potential."},{"time":739208,"text":"Our most recent rover on Mars\nhas discovered traces of organics."},{"time":744747,"text":"Yeah, there are organics\nat the surface of Mars."},{"time":747706,"text":"And it also discovered traces of methane."},{"time":751607,"text":"And we don't know yet\nif the methane in question"},{"time":754152,"text":"is really from geology or biology."},{"time":757990,"text":"Regardless, what we know is\nthat because of the discovery,"},{"time":762859,"text":"the hypothesis that there is still\nlife present on Mars today"},{"time":766100,"text":"remains a viable one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768455,"text":"So by now, I think I have convinced you\nthat Mars is very special to us,"},{"time":773652,"text":"but it would be a mistake to think\nthat Mars is the only place"},{"time":776628,"text":"in the solar system that is interesting\nto find potential microbial life."},{"time":782434,"text":"And the reason is because\nMars and the Earth"},{"time":786352,"text":"could have a common root\nto their tree of life,"},{"time":789143,"text":"but when you go beyond Mars,\nit's not that easy."},{"time":793290,"text":"Celestial mechanics \nis not making it so easy"},{"time":795900,"text":"for an exchange\nof material between planets,"},{"time":798315,"text":"and so if we were to discover\nlife on those planets,"},{"time":802355,"text":"it would be different from us."},{"time":804212,"text":"It would be a different type of life."},{"time":806050,"text":"But in the end, it might be just us,"},{"time":808903,"text":"it might be us and Mars,"},{"time":810899,"text":"or it can be many trees of life\nin the solar system."},{"time":814382,"text":"I don't know the answer yet,\nbut I can tell you something:"},{"time":818110,"text":"No matter what the result is,\nno matter what that magic number is,"},{"time":822542,"text":"it is going to give us a standard"},{"time":824553,"text":"by which we are going to be able \nto measure the life potential,"},{"time":829081,"text":"abundance and diversity\nbeyond our own solar system."},{"time":832191,"text":"And this can be achieved\nby our generation."},{"time":834751,"text":"This can be our legacy,\nbut only if we dare to explore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839654,"text":"Now, finally,"},{"time":841740,"text":"if somebody tells you that looking \nfor alien microbes is not cool"},{"time":845708,"text":"because you cannot have\na philosophical conversation with them,"},{"time":849138,"text":"let me show you why and how\nyou can tell them they're wrong."},{"time":855804,"text":"Well, organic material\nis going to tell you"},{"time":858572,"text":"about environment, about complexity\nand about diversity."},{"time":864231,"text":"DNA, or any information carrier,\nis going to tell you about adaptation,"},{"time":870350,"text":"about evolution, about survival,\nabout planetary changes"},{"time":875371,"text":"and about the transfer of information."},{"time":878219,"text":"All together, they are telling us"},{"time":881307,"text":"what started as a microbial pathway,"},{"time":885208,"text":"and why what started\nas a microbial pathway"},{"time":888226,"text":"sometimes ends up as a civilization"},{"time":891686,"text":"or sometimes ends up as a dead end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":895308,"text":"Look at the solar system,\nand look at the Earth."},{"time":898724,"text":"On Earth, there are many\nintelligent species,"},{"time":901531,"text":"but only one has achieved technology."},{"time":904898,"text":"Right here in the journey\nof our own solar system,"},{"time":908195,"text":"there is a very, very powerful message"},{"time":910934,"text":"that says here's how we should look \nfor alien life, small and big."},{"time":916320,"text":"So yeah, microbes are talking\nand we are listening,"},{"time":919618,"text":"and they are taking us,"},{"time":921337,"text":"one planet at a time\nand one moon at a time,"},{"time":923891,"text":"towards their big brothers out there."},{"time":926770,"text":"And they are telling us about diversity,"},{"time":929486,"text":"they are telling us about\nabundance of life,"},{"time":932110,"text":"and they are telling us\nhow this life has survived thus far"},{"time":936150,"text":"to reach civilization,"},{"time":939192,"text":"intelligence, technology\nand, indeed, philosophy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944174,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":945879,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}